  "notes": "2nd great-grandfather on the Sanderson line. Born in Lenoir County, NC. Father Isaac Sanderson Sr. (1800-1839) died when Isaac was 8. Married Sylvia A. Kennedy in 1857 in Duplin County, NC. Son Ivy Sanderson born 1848 (before marriage — possibly from a prior relationship). Eight children with Sylvia: William Albert (1859-1945), Orpah (1860-1940), Thadius Horry (1866-1913), Leana (1868-), Martha Ann (1870-1952), Isaac Lebbaus (1874-1949), Mary Elizabeth (1877-1947). All born in Duplin County, NC. Died August 5, 1912 at age 81 in Duplin County."
